title: Grateful Dead Live at Deer Creek Music Center on 1993-06-23

Set I

Sting opened

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Vince Welnick - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
